{"tid":456253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"汀九橋半路停車跳橋 財困的士司機送院亡","createTime":"2017-11-02T23:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T00:39:06.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e56779cb9a833a197d4718cb6f1f67d9ed50164a","tid":456253,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T23:09:22.000Z","msg":"凌晨約4時39分，一輛冚旗的士沿青朗公路汀九橋往屯門行駛，至汀九橋中段位置，約50歲司機突然停車，並且離開車廂，攀過圍欄一躍而下，跌落海中及失去蹤影。青馬管制區職員，從閉路電視發現報警。<br />\n<br />\n水警及消防輪到場搜索，約半小時後在橋底附近海面將的士司機救起，送荃灣碼頭轉仁濟醫院急救，惜終告不治。警方在車內發現遺書，正調查事件原因。據知的士司機因金錢問題尋死。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171103/57411165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171103%2F57411165&d=Hltc14%2F7mao1D6uueVlELiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=6a5f94fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171103%2F57411165&h=34456ea6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171103/57411165</a>"},{"pid":"f34425bc2076118e9c9544a8240a2c0e5f858472","tid":456253,"uid":1314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T23:28:48.000Z","msg":"死都死得麻煩過人"},{"pid":"f2b1fd6090ae7e4a6899e164ebde5fb6f9e11168","tid":456253,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T23:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8f0d9a620c64291126c4c3bf6e1042806bd5a6","tid":456253,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T23:54:36.000Z","msg":"好彩深夜,試下返工放工時間跳實俾人屌到翻生"},{"pid":"7eefb1875d5107ba018244466283609fb75c4fc2","tid":456253,"uid":45591,"like":0,"d